+//
+// Configuration:
+//   SOAK_SEED=42                  Deterministic operation sequence (default: 0)
+//   SOAK_PROJECTS=10              Number of projects (default: 10)
+//   SOAK_AGENTS_PER_PROJECT=10   Agents per project (default: 10)
